00:50:49,110 --> 00:50:50,540
Potrebuje operáciu hneď teraz.

745
00:50:50,540 --> 00:50:52,170
Bol to rozkaz.

746
00:50:52,470 --> 00:50:53,470
Choďte do nemocnice Chamyung.

747
00:50:59,510 --> 00:51:00,510
<i>Nie.</i>

